    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artists' brushes that are about the same length as flats. They are round and have tapered points, useful for sketching, outlining, and for fine detail.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000034051/Quick, Artists' and Illustrators' Encyclopedia (1978)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Kunstenaarspenselen die ongeveer dezelfde lengte hebben als platte penselen. Ze zijn rond met  taps toelopende punten en worden gebruikt voor schetsen, aftekenen en voor gedetailleerd werk.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052520/Van Beek Art Supplies</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>與平筆大約等長的畫筆，刷毛呈圓錐形；可用於繪製草圖、勾勒輪廓及描繪細節。
　
</Note_Text>
